Class WinCrypt.CERT_SIMPLE_CHAIN

java.lang.Object
com.sun.jna.Structure
com.sun.jna.platform.win32.WinCrypt.CERT_SIMPLE_CHAIN
Direct Known Subclasses:

Enclosing interface:
WinCrypt
@FieldOrder({"cbSize","TrustStatus","cElement","rgpElement","pTrustListInfo","fHasRevocationFreshnessTime","dwRevocationFreshnessTime"}) public static class WinCrypt.CERT_SIMPLE_CHAIN extends Structure
The CERT_SIMPLE_CHAIN structure contains an array of chain elements and a summary trust status for the chain that the array represents.
